0/shawn-mennenga-stays-with-browns-as-special-teams-assistant|title=Shawn Mennenga Stays With Browns as ST Assistant|last=Pokorny|first=Chris|date=2013-01-30|website=Dawgs By Nature|language=en|access-date=2020-04-11}}</ref>in [[2011 Cleveland Browns season|2011]] <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cleveland.com/browns/2011/02/cleveland_browns_complete_thei.html|title=Cleveland Browns complete their first coaching staff under Pat Shurmur|last=Cabot|first=Mary Kay|last2=clevel|date=2011-02-15|website=cleveland|language=en|access-date=2020-04-11|last3=.com}}</ref> under [[Pat Shurmur]] after years of college coaching experience. During 2018 Shawn became the special teams coordinator for [[Vanderbilt Commodores football|Vanderbilt]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://vanderbilthustler.com/16762/featured/derek-mason-seeking-revamped-special-teams-look-under-shawn-mennenga/|title=Derek Mason seeking revamped special teams look under Shawn Mennenga|last=Klein|first=Cutler|website=The Vanderbilt Hustler|access-date=2020-04-11}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://fanbuzz.com/college-football/sec/vanderbilt-shawn-menneng-special-teams/|title=SEC program steals away NFL coach with latest reported hire|last=Nardone|first=Joseph|date=2018-01-28|website=FanBuzz - Sports News - NFL {{!}} NCAA {{!}} NBA {{!}}  WWE|language=en|access-date=2020-04-11}}</ref> before ultimately returning to the NFL<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.12up.com/posts/6285338-report-packers-hire-shawn-mennenga-as-new-special-teams-coach|title=REPORT: Packers Hire Shawn Mennenga as New Special Teams Coach|date=2019-01-31|website=12up.com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-11}}</ref>.\n\n== Family ==\nMennenga and his wife, Christie, have a son, Garrett, and a daughter, Ashley.<ref name=\":0\" />\n\n==References==\n[[Category:Cleveland Browns coaches]]\n[[Category:Green Bay Packers coaches]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Iowa]]\n[[Category:Vanderbilt Commodores coaches]]\n[[Category:Vanderbilt Commodores 